WEBVTT

00:04:27.739 --> 00:04:30.965
is both a product of nature
and a law of nature,

00:04:30.989 --> 00:04:33.691
regardless of whether it's in our bodies

00:04:33.715 --> 00:04:35.753
or sitting in the bottom of a test tube.

00:04:36.523 --> 00:04:37.978
As we delved into this issue,

00:04:38.002 --> 00:04:41.910
we traveled all over the country
to speak with many different experts --

00:04:42.588 --> 00:04:46.301
scientists, medical professionals,
lawyers, patent lawyers.

00:04:46.753 --> 00:04:50.663
Most of them agreed that we were right
as a matter of policy,

00:04:50.687 --> 00:04:53.472
and, at least in theory,
as a matter of law.

00:04:54.313 --> 00:04:55.468
All of them thought

00:04:55.492 --> 00:04:58.062
our chances of winning
a gene-patent challenge

00:04:58.086 --> 00:04:59.953
were about zero.